	<summary>Administrator Tool for cleaning up the logfile</summary>
	<description><![CDATA[**Administration tool for cleaning up the log file**

- ✅ Only accessible for administration.
- ✅ Error levels with different colors.
- ✅ Number of displayed log entries can be set.
- ✅ After correcting a log entry it can be deleted from the log file.
- ✅ One click deletion of all duplicates within the log file.
- ✅ Empty the log file without using shell commands.]]></description>
